{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1929, "height": 2607, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "东张村", "block_bbox": [893, 229, 1171, 291], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "东张村位于渑池县仁村乡东南四公里处，是渑池县仁村乡的一个建制村。原称张村，以同县的张村镇也有一同名之村而称。下辖东张村、西张村、寨南等3个自然村。东张村背靠小虎坡，面对青龙山，东张村古来是形胜之地，南边原有奎星楼、龙王庙、奶奶庙各一座，当地流传有小虎坡的传说故事。2007年由中铝公司投资修建一条宽30多米的人工河道，河道两旁十米多宽的沿海大道全部铺成柏油路面。杜氏家族从仁村乡大水沟村迁移至此，其迁入世系为：", "block_bbox": [302, 357, 1758, 709], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "流芳公——忠——果—真银——三元—乘龙——兰——彬——允法—朝选——林邦——文秀——荣升——林清—作栋\n", "block_bbox": [302, 731, 1751, 843], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "林富—作新", "block_bbox": [947, 985, 1196, 1032], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "原迁入时仅十几口人，现已发展到一百多口人，占全村人口的六分之一，高中以上学历占杜氏人口的30%，其中北京大学学历一人，正县级干部一人，正科级干部一人。\n", "block_bbox": [303, 1048, 1748, 1218], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一八七", "block_bbox": [151, 1967, 199, 2070], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "aside_text", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [142, 686, 216, 1354], "block_id": 6, "block_order": null}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9017742276191711, "coordinate": [303.078369140625, 1048.383544921875, 1748.766845703125, 1218.733154296875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8567431569099426, "coordinate": [302.08538818359375, 357.7523193359375, 1758.43408203125, 709.8609619140625]}, {"cls_i